	(1, 0, NULL, '{\"name\":\"文字版\",\"type\":\"text\",\"seg\":12,\"pre_seg\":0,\"cont\":{\"show\":true,\"space\":false,\"text\":\"<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \\\"-\\/\\/W3C\\/\\/DTD HTML 4.0 Transitional\\/\\/EN\\\" \\\"http:\\/\\/www.w3.org\\/TR\\/REC-html40\\/loose.dtd\\\">\\n<html><body>\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center; \\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 24px;\\\">漫漫創業路，<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size: 24px;\\\">別再選擇單打獨鬥<\\/span><\\/p>\\n<table class=\\\"table table-bordered\\\"><tbody>\\n<tr>\\n<td><br><\\/td>\\n<td><span style=\\\"font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(189, 148, 0);\\\">創業自己是老闆<\\/span><\\/td>\\n<td><span style=\\\"font-size: 18px;\\\"> 上班 別人安排按部就班<\\/span><\\/td>\\n<\\/tr>\\n<tr>\\n<td>\\n<p style=\\\"line-height: 1;\\\">工作 <\\/p>\\n<p style=\\\"line-height: 1;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color: transparent;\\\">內容           <\\/span><\\/p>\\n<\\/td>\\n<td><span style=\\\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(74, 123, 140);\\\">多元變化有趣<\\/span><\\/td>\\n<td>工作內容較為單一<\\/td>\\n<\\/tr>\\n<tr>\\n<td>\\n<p style=\\\"line-height: 1;\\\">職涯<\\/p>\\n<p style=\\\"line-height: 1;\\\">發展<\\/p>\\n<\\/td>\\n<td><span style=\\\"color: rgb(74, 123, 140); font-weight: bold;\\\">個人品牌擁有者<\\/span><\\/td>\\n<td>執行分內工作小職員<\\/td>\\n<\\/tr>\\n<tr>\\n<td>\\n<p style=\\\"line-height: 1;\\\">職場<\\/p>\\n<p style=\\\"line-height: 1;\\\">角色<br>\\n<\\/p>\\n<\\/td>\\n<td>一人多工的<span style=\\\"color: rgb(74, 123, 140); font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px;\\\">品牌創辦人<\\/span>\\n<\\/td>\\n<td>階層分工工具人<\\/td>\\n<\\/tr>\\n<tr>\\n<td><p style=\\\"line-height: 1;\\\">思維<\\/p><\\/td>\\n<td>\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(74, 123, 140);\\\">主動去思考<\\/span><br>\\n<\\/td>\\n<td>被動思考<\\/td>\\n<\\/tr>\\n<tr>\\n<td>機會<\\/td>\\n<td><span style=\\\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(74, 123, 140);\\\">遇見機會，會去思考該如何著手資源找解決方案<\\/span><\\/td>\\n<td>沒資源會無法行動，等上層安排資源，只會把事情擱在一邊<\\/td>\\n<\\/tr>\\n<\\/tbody><\\/table>\\n<p><br><\\/p>\\n<p>\\n<\\/p>\\n<p>\\n<\\/p>\\n<p>\\n<\\/p>\\n<p>\\n<\\/p>\\n